ta-base-url=3D"https://mews.atlassian.net/wiki" data-linked-resource-conten=
t-type=3D"image/png" data-linked-resource-container-id=3D"1941537376" data-=
linked-resource-container-version=3D"7" data-media-id=3D"f0ef93ca-13b5-4669=
-8e58-e7200369ff92" data-media-type=3D"file" height=3D"238"></span>
<p local-id=3D"ab5c088a1d37"></p>
<div id=3D"expander-1671198568" class=3D"expand-container">
<div id=3D"expander-control-1671198568" class=3D"expand-control">
<span class=3D"expand-control-icon"><img style=3D"vertical-align:middle;" c=
lass=3D"expand-control-image" src=3D"ca6da21f5838dbc0da0eac444a9e81689b0300=
b454f5edfdc99e7241a00b9231" width=3D"16" height=3D"16"></span><span class=
=3D"expand-control-text">Original, pre-annotation plan</span>
</div>
<div id=3D"expander-content-1671198568" class=3D"expand-content">
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
<pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"brush=
: java; gutter: false; theme: Confluence" data-theme=3D"Confluence"># Daily=
 Digest Blitz Test Plan

## Context

Daily Digest is a Commander page that surfaces Smart Task suggestions for a=
 given date window so a user can triage them at the start of their shift. I=
t supports filtering (date range up to 7 days, departments, loyalty tier, V=
IP, search by guest name), three view modes (desktop grid, desktop list, mo=
bile swipe), an accept/reject flow with a 5-second undo window, and a guest=
 detail panel. Backend is `agt-core`'s `GET /smartTasks/dailyDigest` plus `=
POST /smartTasks/{create,reject}`.

The goal of this session: spin up the local stack, drive the page in a real=
 browser via Playwright MCP, exercise as many distinct behaviors and edge c=
ases as possible in one sitting, and produce a structured findings log. We =
want signal on real bugs, regressions, and rough edges before any further i=
nvestment in the feature.

A pass through this plan should produce: (1) a stack-up checklist confirmed=
, (2) a populated findings markdown with screenshots, (3) at minimum a yes/=
no on the suspected pagination truncation issue.

## Pre-flight gate

Confirm the dev DB has Daily Digest suggestions for enterprise `9173ac0f-7f=
88-4f5b-8bba-b310006b0da0` in `today =E2=86=92 today+7`. There is no seed e=
ndpoint =E2=80=94 suggestions are produced by the agent pipeline and persis=
ted to `smart_task_events` (status=3DPENDING). Quick check via Swagger:

```
GET http://localhost:8000/smartTasks/dailyDigest?enterpriseId=3D9173ac0f-7f=
88-4f5b-8bba-b310006b0da0&amp;chainId=3D...&amp;dueDateStart=3D&lt;today&gt=
;&amp;dueDateEnd=3D&lt;today+7&gt;
```

If the response is empty: (a) try running the task_creator agent against up=
coming reservations, (b) insert rows directly into `smart_task_events` mirr=
oring an existing pending row, or (c) document blocked rows as `BLOCKED:no-=
data` and continue with the rest.

## Setup

Follow the existing `smart-tasks-browser-e2e` skill for stack spin-up. Delt=
as specific to Daily Digest:

- `packages/commander/web-app/src/localFeatureFlags.ts` =E2=80=94 verify `d=
ailyDigestEnabled: true` AND `opDailyDigestEnabled: true`. Both default tru=
e; confirm, don't assume.
- `packages/commander/web-app/dev/index.html:57` =E2=80=94 `agentsServiceUr=
l: 'http://localhost:8000'`.
- Start agt-core: `docker compose up -d` from `~/github/agt-core`. `curl ht=
tp://localhost:8000/health`. If JSONDecodeError on startup: `docker compose=
 restart agt-core`.
- Start commander: `yarn workspace mews-commander start` =E2=86=92 `http://=
localhost:8080`.
- Login: `qa-automation-global-admin@mews.com` (1Password).
- Direct URL: `http://localhost:8080/Commander/9173ac0f-7f88-4f5b-8bba-b310=
006b0da0/DailyDigest`.
- Apply AssistantContainer pointer-events neutralizer on every page load (p=
er skill).

## Coverage matrix

P0 =3D blocks usage, P1 =3D degrades, P2 =3D polish.

