| Pg1 | Pagination | Seed 25+ confirmed-reservation suggestions in window |=
 Only 18 returned, no "load more" UI =E2=80=94 likely real bug | P0 |
| Pg2 | Pagination | Backend sends `nextCursor`, frontend never sends it ba=
ck | Confirm in network =E2=80=94 silent truncation | P1 |
| So1 | Sort | date-asc =E2=86=92 date-desc | Reorders without refetch | P1=
