These are already-filed tickets. If encountered during testing, note them a=
s "known" rather than new findings.

| Ticket | Status | Summary |
|--------|--------|---------|
| AGT-1092 | New | No Undo affordance for desktop Accept/Reject; mutation f=
ires immediately |
