ot happen |
| AGT-1096 | New | Tweener viewport (~415-768px) hides toggle but doesn't e=
ngage swipe layout |
| AGT-1097 | New | Clear filters snaps date range to today instead of truly=
 clearing |
| AGT-1098 | New | Returning guest / Loyalty / Complaint not exposed as fil=
ter options |
| AGT-1099 | New | Accept toast says "Created" instead of user-facing copy =
|
| AGT-1075 | New | Undo only works for mobile swipe, not desktop buttons or=
 panel |
| AGT-1077 | Review | Date range not respected on page refresh |
| AGT-1060 | New | "No results" message is unpolished |
| AGT-1064 | Review | Configurable default filters (in progress) |
| AGT-1039 | To Do | Missing one-time swipe tip on mobile (Gainsight) |
| AGT-1042 | To Do | Side panel should include reservation info |
| AGT-1062 | New | Accessibility audit needed |
| AGT-1066 | New | Arrival/departure times unclear, date semantics ambiguou=
s |
