## Execution Order

**Phase 1 =E2=80=94 Verify core works (P0, ~10 min)**
- 1.1=E2=80=931.4: Load, skeleton, empty state, error
- 10.1: Accept one card, observe toast text and undo availability
- If undo exists: 10.2 to reverse. If not: note as known (AGT-1092), stop d=
estructive tests.

**Phase 2 =E2=80=94 Filters &amp; sorting (P1, ~15 min)**
- 2.1=E2=80=932.23: All filter combinations, sorting, known issues verifica=
tion
- 3.1=E2=80=933.4: Pagination via scrolling

**Phase 3 =E2=80=94 Mobile &amp; tweener (P1, ~10 min)**
- 7.1=E2=80=937.9: Viewport resize, swipe gestures, undo (mobile has undo)
- 8.1=E2=80=938.2: Tweener viewport gap

**Phase 4 =E2=80=94 Desktop views &amp; panel (P2, ~10 min)**
- 5.1=E2=80=935.8: Grid view
- 6.1=E2=80=936.4: List view
- 9.1=E2=80=939.9: Detail panel content

**Phase 5 =E2=80=94 Cross-tab &amp; responsive (P2, ~10 min)**
- 12.1=E2=80=9312.3: Multi-tab behavior
- 13.1=E2=80=9313.6: Breakpoint transitions

**Phase 6 =E2=80=94 Edge cases &amp; a11y (P3, ~10 min)**
- 14.1=E2=80=9314.5: Stress/edge cases
- 15.1=E2=80=9315.5: Keyboard/accessibility

---

## Test Count Summary

| Priority | Count | Destructive | Read-only |
|----------|-------|-------------|-----------|
| P0 | 10 | 4 (try undo first) | 6 |
| P1 | 19 | 3 (mobile undo available) | 16 |
| P2 | 25 | 1 (with undo attempt) | 24 |
| P3 | 10 | 0 | 10 |
| **Total** | **64** | **8** | **56** |

&gt; Destructive actions minimized. Desktop undo expected missing (AGT-1092=
) =E2=80=94 extra caution there. Mobile undo works. At most 2-3 suggestions=
 permanently consumed.
</pre>
