<p local-id=3D"4d37f22891e4"><strong>Tier 0:</strong> all 11 P0 rows reache=
d; 1 finding (E5).</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"a73bf54e-1b24-436c-bf28-6c83a3808ebf">
<p local-id=3D"faba4f02d163"><strong>Tier 1:</strong> ~15 of 35 rows execut=
ed; the rest are doable but were not the highest-value items left in the bu=
dget. Main findings around search-not-live (Finding 6), tier-pill mismatch =
(Finding 7), URL-state-IS-persisted (Finding 3), and the nested-button HTML=
 (Finding 4).</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"87ee670b-3f49-4df3-9b2a-493bb9dd23ad">
<p local-id=3D"e0add6aeef06"><strong>Tier 2:</strong> mobile swipe untestab=
le on this MCP/host. Drawer + button-driven mutation flows verified. Most c=
onsequential finding of the session: <strong>no Undo affordance on desktop =
or tablet</strong> (Finding 9).</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"d5277695-65e9-41df-abd7-04418883a58a">
<p local-id=3D"7892a2f07bb1"><strong>Tier 3:</strong> deferred =E2=80=94 ma=
ny items were dependent on the missing Undo flow.</p></li>
</ul>
