<h3 local-id=3D"89ca933a20e3" id=3D"BlitzTestingDailyDigestwithClaude-Whatt=
odonext">What to do next</h3>
<ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"20960000-04af-4101-a00d-9b7301723d6a">
<li local-id=3D"cf854219-f167-4858-8a55-d92b49c79450">
<p local-id=3D"c832307d483c">Engineering: confirm whether the undo flow is =
supposed to be engaged in this build (Finding 9). This drives all of Tier 3=
.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"1f627647-c447-4593-bd4a-815a8c444231">
<p local-id=3D"42964c2e7e31">Engineering: tighten the responsive breakpoint=
s (Finding 11) so the swipe layer is reachable on real mobile widths and th=
e toggle returns at narrow tablet widths.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"f40d7942-12b8-4faf-ae94-8f463e803593">
<p local-id=3D"0380b996e6f9">Design/Copy: align the success toast to "Sugge=
stion accepted" / "Suggestion dismissed" pair (Finding 10).</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"d38bde62-f76b-43d9-920b-1f13599066f7">
<p local-id=3D"bbbe60e16ad9">Re-run with seeded data &gt; 25 cards to actua=
lly exercise pagination (Pg1/2/3).</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"b78bb682-ee53-4098-a18d-1f8c2326eed6">
<p local-id=3D"7531c2cbe3e8">Re-run with Chrome DevTools MCP installed (or =
<code>playwright</code> running in real touch-event mode) to land Sw* + N1=
=E2=80=93N5.</p></li>
</ol>
