ssionSummary(fromClaude,withChromeDevTools):">2nd Session Summary (from Cla=
ude, with Chrome DevTools):</h2>
<ul local-id=3D"09f3d622-563c-4740-90e9-2951e737deb4">
<li local-id=3D"281f8365-7c80-4a72-bee9-e8b951e1b627">
<p local-id=3D"71c739dcf894">Tester: <a class=3D"external-link" href=3D"mai=
