<h3 local-id=3D"7c9cefae033b" id=3D"BlitzTestingDailyDigestwithClaude-3rdSe=
ssionFindings">3rd Session Findings</h3>
<ul local-id=3D"e00ae350-8bff-4732-b274-31035fe40db4">
<li local-id=3D"9329b0de-4bdf-4703-a79f-e2a3041686cc">
<p local-id=3D"d93be0223c9b"><strong>1 new critical finding:</strong> Deskt=
op accept has zero feedback (no toast, no undo, silent mutation)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"65b2d806-e603-4c0b-a872-1fde255b8fd2">
<p local-id=3D"7180eaf36032"><strong>1 ticket potentially fixed:</strong> A=
GT-1094 (nested buttons not reproduced)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"f5b6df92-4198-4d39-ada9-42c9046c2600">
<p local-id=3D"778b39aedc89"><strong>8 known issues confirmed</strong> from=
 Jira</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"af62d1d4-c243-43a5-8d83-79e3a02899d2">
<p local-id=3D"4b50e1b6d215"><strong>21 tests passed</strong> across grid, =
list, filters, sorting, panel, mobile, edge cases</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"a943a368-78a3-4626-9d3f-230b9291ca8e">
<p local-id=3D"3ca9d2d005e1"><strong>6 areas need manual testing</strong> (=
swipe, cross-tab, keyboard nav, pagination, screen reader)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"6872408d-9fde-4f68-a1c2-495bc8f72326">
<p local-id=3D"7ad8116c9018"><strong>1 suggestion permanently consumed</str=
ong> during testing (Dmitri Volkov =E2=80=94 king-bed room)</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"d1d2e34ba741"><strong>Priority recommendation:</strong> Fix =
AGT-1092 (desktop undo/toast) before any broader rollout. The silent, irrev=
ersible accept is a data-integrity risk for users who misclick.</p>
<p local-id=3D"50aeca0ecd5e">Full details <a href=3D"https://mews.atlassian=
